Alright, you're here. The reason why demons
appeared in the city the other day is because the
\C[2] barrier pillars \C[0] here were damaged.

If these barrier pillars are damaged, the barrier
weakens and those guys will invade the city.
That's why we need to repair them as soon as
possible.

While I'm repairing them, I'm counting on you to
protect us from those guys.

The barrier pillars are installed on the east and
west sides, so it doesn't matter which side you
approach from.
Alright, understood. Let's do our best!

attack.
